    "name": "Laundry Service Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3203190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/52e1821786c54d4e0a56eec39745f43b.webp?t=1770405892\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/52e1821786c54d4e0a56eec39745f43b.poster.avif?t=1770405892\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=175 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>洗衣服务模拟器是一款轻松的第一人称模拟游戏，让您体验管理洗衣店，应对大量顾客（和他们的脏衣服）。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/92006b9bd0bcf3abe920e1aa9cb8f2b6.avif?t=1770405892\" width=800 height=101 /></span>快来组织起来吧！打造最佳的洗衣店设计并管理您的店铺。在完美的洗衣环境中迎接顾客，展示您的清洁技艺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/b67e27bae416192b9f9880da4f60354c.avif?t=1770405892\" width=800 height=101 /></span>从零到英雄！购买高科技机器，更快更好地清洗所有衣物。将设备从廉价机器升级到高速洗衣机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/39f386ae679e291b665a7621f16bef96.avif?t=1770405892\" width=800 height=101 /></span>洗衣粉用完了？时刻补充大量洗衣粉，别忘了尝试超级清洁化学品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/2d6d77905f7520c4bf24815fd41aa125.avif?t=1770405892\" width=800 height=101 /></span>很简单，越干净赚得越多。所以，脏衣服越多，现金越多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203190/extras/80ede99956e8cbf7bbc4f38445e7b70f.avif?t=1770405892\" width=800 height=101 /></span>打破墙壁！开辟新空间，为您的洗衣店增加更多机器和顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《洗衣服务模拟器》中，与每家洗衣店一样，顾客满意度至关重要。您必须保持一切整洁，购买新机器，设定合理的服务价格，并发展您的洗衣店以避免破产。</strong></p>",
